items.sentence: You aren't getting away from me that easily, Tom.
You aren't going to believe what happened to Tom.
Tom will have a heart attack if he isn't careful.
Tom told me that he isn't going to do that again.
Tom knows he isn't supposed to help Mary do that.
Tom doesn't know he isn't supposed to park there.
I don't care what Tom does when he isn't at work.
You don't have to pretend that you're interested.
Tom was the last person to cross the finish line.
I hope the new plan will work out satisfactorily.
